body.name: YITAHOME L Shaped Desk with Drawers, 55“ Corner Computer Desk with Power Outlets & LED Lights, Home Office Desk with Bookshelf, White
features: Convenient Charging Station: This L-shaped computer desk features 2 USB ports, 4 power outlets & a 6.56ft power cord to charge your laptop, tablet, printer and other devices, making your life easier

Cool & Smart LED Light Strips: Our L-shaped desk features a beautiful RGB LED light strip, flexibly controlled by a phone app or remote control, and you can customize any color you like via app. Plus, choose from various modes including music sync and timer functions to enhance the mood and inspire creativity while working

Ample Storage Space: 2-in-1 corner desk combines a computer desk with a file cabinets featuring 1 file drawer with adjustable hanging bars for letter, A4, legal size files, 2 drawers for small office supplies, and 2 bottom open storage shelves with 3-heights adjustable for different heights item. Also, the spacious upper open shelf can be also used as printer stand holding printers, scanners, fax machines or any other office machines within your reach to improve working efficiency

Maximize Your Workspace: Enjoy ample working space with our white computer desk with a wide desktop of 55.1”L x 19.68”W, which can hold many office supplies, such as monitors, table lamp, books, files, etc.

Sturdy & Durable: The white corner desk made of high-grade P2 MDF board with a scratch-resistant finish that protects the desktop from daily wear and tears, and 1.57" x 0.79" heavy-duty metal frame, ensures excellent stability, durability and longevity for years of use, which would meet the various daily load-bearing needs.
